hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64e97f47b13b8057d0b9eb50622e3bde9a66ae5","tid":909114,"uid":156363,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T06:58:00.000Z","msg":"讀開星奮真"},{"pid":"6c2f2b46149f6cd1c3969e0c2504aaed15687a94","tid":909114,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:03:09.000Z","msg":"香港政府係用分，台灣就用份<br />\n<br />\n身分證 (identity card)指根據本條例發給的身分證，並包括永久性居民身分證<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap177\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap177&d=GLHxB1Bl6fk81vWTn2Ta6%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=282d9916\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap177</a>"},{"pid":"056a23e583242e02f7895f3f0592741f16837523","tid":909114,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:06:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec869a8e457dbf2b17095b212fdf484e8be0ea13","tid":909114,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:06:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港<del>政府</del>法例係用分，政府就用份<br />\n<br />\n身分證 (identity card)指根據本條例發給的身分證，並包括永久性居民身分證<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap177\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap177&d=GLHxB1Bl6fk81vWTn2Ta6%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=282d9916\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap177</a></blockquote><br />\n香港身份證之中文名稱曾經惹起爭論，《香港特別行政區基本法》中採用「身份證」[2]，《人事登記條例》則採用「身分證」[3]。不過，香港政府從英國屬土時代已經採用「身份證」為中文名稱，而香港立法會亦通過繼續使用「身份證」為中文名稱，香港文字研究者容若亦認為「份」為正字。因此，1991年香港政府計劃將「身份」復古為「身分」的時候，容若與陸離等等人士大力反對。因而惹起支持「份」和「分」的不同人士展開辯論，最後香港政府維持原有寫法。"},{"pid":"8520c715f1e55dbc4bdf0a50b7a84f9096f0a3f7","tid":909114,"uid":106675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c2f2b46149f6cd1c3969e0c2504aaed15687a94","tid":909114,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:03:09.000Z","msg":"香港政府係用分，台灣就用份<br />\n<br />\n身分證 (identity card)指根據本條例發給的身分證，並包括永久性居民身分證<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap177\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap177&d=GLHxB1Bl6fk81vWTn2Ta6%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=282d9916\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap177</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0745d15b75d041822d4611a1f1a96910a1d58b91","tid":909114,"uid":130879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:08:51.000Z","msg":"身分點讀"},{"pid":"33ffe015e6bb9ffd84d27384805e41f5f1d17be4","tid":909114,"uid":42636,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:13:48.000Z","msg":"d 新鄉港人讀：新粉震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdeb33e4c5fc44a821a0bdefa59e2ff7c5519aa5","tid":909114,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:14:34.000Z","msg":"讀開鮮分精"},{"pid":"19b2b76fff982d92c484af71b9218779023946ea","tid":909114,"uid":116330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:20:47.000Z","msg":"生飯正"}]}